TITLE: VS Code I18n Ally Custom Framework Configuration
DESCRIPTION: Configuration file to integrate with the VS Code I18n Ally extension, enabling features like go-to-definition and inline previews.
SOURCE: https://github.com/wxt-dev/wxt/blob/main/packages/i18n/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_23

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
# An array of strings which contain Language Ids defined by VS Code
# You can check available language ids here: https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/languages/identifiers
languageIds:
  - typescript
  - typescriptreact

# Look for t("...")
usageMatchRegex:
  - "[^\\w\\d]t\\(['\"`]({key})['\"`]"

# Disable other built-in i18n ally frameworks
monopoly: true
```

