TITLE: Updating i18n Translation Usage in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates the change in usage of the i18n.t() function, removing the options argument and manually escaping the '<' symbol.
SOURCE: https://github.com/wxt-dev/wxt/blob/main/packages/i18n/CHANGELOG.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
